These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing, baking, puzzles
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, sports, epic, adventure
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, helicopter, skateboard, van
1. the person driving the trike is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
5. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the van is between the person watching adventure movies and the person who's hobby is collecting##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | puzzles      | collecting | rock-climbing | baking |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | musical  | sports   | adventure    |
| Transport     | trike     | skateboard    | van    | helicopter      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, hiking, traveling, gardening
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, thai, australian, pakistani
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, train, snowmobile, scooter
1. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is the australian##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the thai##1
7. the canadian is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
8. the pakistani is between the thai and the person who's hobby is traveling##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | gardening | traveling   | hiking | writing  |
| Nationality   | australian     | canadian | pakistani  | thai |
| Transport     | scooter        | snowmobile  | train    | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, mango, asparagus, plum
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, indonesian, egyptian, pakistani
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, trike, taxi, quad-bike
1. the pakistani is between the person eating cauliflower and the person eating plum##2
2. the indonesian is the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is the person eating asparagus##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the person eating plum is in an odd position##4
6. the egyptian is between the person eating mango and the nigerian##2
7. the pakistani is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | cauliflower | mango   | plum     | asparagus     |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | pakistani | egyptian   | nigerian  |
| Transport     | quad-bike      | trike | taxi | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, thriller, time-travel, adventure
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, hip-hop, r&b, trance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, skateboarding, parkour, swimming
1. the fan of trance is in an even position##4
2. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
5. the fan of trance is the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is the fan of blues##1
7. the fan of r&b is the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | adventure   | time-travel     | thriller |
| Music-Genre   | r&b  | trance      | blues        | hip-hop     |
| Sport         | parkour | baseball | swimming | skateboarding   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, indonesian, mexican, australian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, cricket, surfing, soccer
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, subway, quad-bike, scooter
1. the australian is the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the mexican is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the roller is the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
7. the indonesian is on the far right##1
8. the mexican is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
9. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | australian   | mexican | indonesian |
| Sport         | cricket      | soccer | sailing      | surfing |
| Transport     | subway | roller        | scooter       | quad-bike  |

