.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, blueberry, papaya, cucumber
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, dancing, collecting, photography
4 different pets are kept: frog, bird, rabbit, cat
1. the person eating blueberry is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the owner of the frog is the person eating blueberry##1
4. the person eating papaya is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
6. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
7. the person eating cucumber is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | papaya   | cucumber      | blueberry       | kale |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | photography | collecting     | dancing |
| Pet     | cat     | bird  | frog | rabbit |

