.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, water, cola, mirinda
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, family, crime, adventure
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, dog, cat, snake
1. the owner of the cat is the person watching epic movies##1
2. the owner of the dog is between the person watching adventure movies and the owner of the rabbit##2
3. the person watching adventure movies is the person drinking water##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
5. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
7. the person watching epic movies is the person drinking milk##1
8. the owner of the cat is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | cola   | mirinda          | water | milk        |
| Movie-Genre   | crime     | family | adventure   | epic     |
| Pet           | rabbit | dog         | snake         | cat |

