.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, photography, rock-climbing, cooking
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, pilot, writer, police-officer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, classical, punk, reggae
1. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
2. the writer is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the police-officer is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the fan of punk##1
5. the fan of classical is between the analyst and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
6. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the writer##3
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | photography | gardening      | rock-climbing       | cooking    |
| Job           | pilot  | writer  | police-officer | analyst |
| Music-Genre   | reggae      | punk | classical         | funk    |

