.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, tea, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, writer, accountant, photographer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, golf, cricket, rowing
1. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the police-officer##1
7. the police-officer is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
8. the writer is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
9. the photographer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | almond-milk         | mirinda  | tea     | hot-chocolate         |
| Job        | photographer | writer | police-officer | accountant         |
| Sport      | golf         | cricket  | sailing   | rowing |

