.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, salsa, techno, pop
There are 4 different nationalities: american, dutch, chinese, spanish
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, goat, hamster, goldfish
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
 2. the american is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the goat is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 4. the chinese is between the fan of salsa and the fan of trance##2
 5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
 6. the owner of the goldfish is the fan of techno##1
 7. the spanish is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of trance is in an odd position##4
 9. the dutch is between the fan of pop and the fan of techno##2
10. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | techno    | salsa | pop    |
| Nationality   | american | chinese | dutch  | spanish |
| Pet           | hamster   | goldfish    | hedgehog        | goat   |

