.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, cola, milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, videographer, coach, entrepreneur
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, thai, japanese, malaysian
1. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
2. the videographer is on the left of the nurse##1
3. the malaysian is on the left or right of the coach##3
4. the videographer is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the nurse##1
6. the malaysian is on the right of the videographer##1
7. the thai is on the left of the videographer##1
8. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the thai##3
9. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | coffee                | milk  | hot-chocolate | cola   |
| Job           | entrepreneur | videographer | nurse   | coach |
| Nationality   | thai         | australian     | malaysian     | japanese |

