1. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the person eating garlic is on the far left##1
3. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
4. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
5. the fan of techno is between the person watching mystery movies and the fan of rock##2
6. the person watching fantasy movies is in an even position##4
7. the person eating kale is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
