.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, juice, cola
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, italian, malaysian, indian
4 different pets are kept: snake, chinchilla, mouse, bird
1. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person drinking juice and the egyptian##2
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
3. the malaysian is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
4. the owner of the bird is on the left of the italian##1
5. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
7. the egyptian is on the left or right of the indian##3
8. the malaysian is the person drinking iced-tea##1
9. the indian is between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the snake##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | juice      | lemonade  | cola    |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | italian | indian | egyptian |
| Pet           | bird      | mouse       | chinchilla   | snake      |

