There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, french, canadian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, tennis, weightlifting, parkour
1. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's sport is climbing##2
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
6. the canadian is between the person who's sport is climbing and the dutch##2
7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
8. the egyptian is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is climbing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | fishing    | writing | filmmaking  | collecting  |
| Nationality   | french | egyptian       | canadian | dutch |
| Sport         | weightlifting   | climbing      | parkour | tennis       |

