3. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
5. the person drinking juice is between the person driving the trike and the person who's sport is golf##2
6. the person driving the taxi is the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | iced-tea    | juice     | fanta    | 7up        |
| Sport       | golf   | climbing | skateboarding | cycling |
| Transport   | helicopter | motorbike      | trike    | taxi   |

