.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, peas, artichoke, pumpkin
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, writing, card-games, traveling
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, rabbit, ferret
1. the person eating raspberry is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the person eating artichoke is on the far left##1
5. the person eating peas is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
8. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | artichoke    | peas    | raspberry  | pumpkin |
| Hobby   | traveling | writing | dancing | card-games      |
| Pet     | frog   | dog        | ferret   | rabbit       |

 